data.description: Experience coastal living at its finest in this charming newly remodeled fully furnished 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located just moments away from the tranquil waters. The highlight of this property is undoubtedly the private hot tub, game room, large entertainment deck that will provide you with a luxurious retreat right in your own backyard. With modern amenities, ample living space, and a convenient location to the beach, this home is a must-see for those seeking a cozy oasis. The home also will come with a golf cart, security cameras and an alarm system.
